{"tid":1510633,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"當警察開槍是克制 - 曾志豪","createTime":"2019-08-27T09:08:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T09:23:18.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8bf20d0c75bcee339a53ebfce0be7845f2022e43","tid":1510633,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T09:08:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9B%BE%E5%BF%97%E8%B1%AA/daily/article/20190827/20756356\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259B%25BE%25E5%25BF%2597%25E8%25B1%25AA%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190827%2F20756356&d=9rGlslGXeLGLpJWMZA8bi7eFZk%2BLn%2Bp4m9s6a9hK%2BPA%3D&h=16f2d11b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259B%25BE%25E5%25BF%2597%25E8%25B1%25AA%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190827%2F20756356&h=58b50ecf\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9B%BE%E5%BF%97%E8%B1%AA/daily/article/20190827/20756356</a><br />\n<br />\n當警察開槍是克制 - 曾志豪<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20190827/large/1566806510_8982.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20190827%2Flarge%2F1566806510_8982.jpg&h=ce68c398&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港警察已經團結到空前絕後的程度，當示威者以「核爆都唔割席」互相鼓勵，警察身先士卒，示範了何謂「開槍都唔割席」的齊心。<br />\n<br />\n荃灣黑夜，警察掏出左輪手槍，開火。之後，指嚇現場記者。<br />\n<br />\n終於來到警察開槍的時刻。警方深夜馬上召開記者會，比起元朗721的效率高了不知多少倍。當大家以為警方會難以解釋開槍行為，畢竟面前示威者只有雨傘棍棒，和元朗白衣人的藤條水喉通差不多，比起荃灣刀手斬人的凶器相比，又差得遠了。如果警方面對斬人的刀手也可以收歛沒有動槍，那麼面對雨傘和長棒，照計應付得綽綽有餘。<br />\n<br />\n誰知警方的回答是：警員生命受到威脅，所以開槍， 是英勇克制。<br />\n<br />\n生命受威脅？你說的是，右眼被射爆眼的少女嗎？被刀手斬腳見骨的市民嗎？被元朗白衣人打到遍體鱗傷的街坊嗎？還是，被水炮車攻擊的香港人？這些人生命才真的受到威脅了，他們是否也能合法使用致命武器還擊？<br />\n<br />\n警方拔槍指向示威者，其實是因為有警員跌槍，他們害怕會被人混亂搶槍，所以便方寸大亂，圍圈執槍，然後三槍並舉指向市民和記者。<br />\n<br />\n跌槍執槍，有甚麼英勇？持槍指向記者，有甚麼英勇？一腳把正下跪的市民踢翻，有甚麼英勇？還要辯解這是自然反應！即是說，警方見到市民的自然反應就是要打人？這點警察倒很誠實。<br />\n<br />\n克制是已經控制得相當好，原來警察覺得開槍已經算克制，那甚麼叫「放肆」呢？開槍打死人還叫克制嗎？<br />\n<br />\n六四的屠城，連坦克都出動，那究竟是英勇還是克制？<br />\n<br />\n這種盲撐已經成為一種風土病，阿Sir「無後顧之憂」還不夠，還要橫行到幾時？ <br />\n<br />\n曾志豪<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n累己累人 (邁克)<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n誰是真暴徒？ (高慧然)"},{"pid":"7e422a67faa8853d85e3705c6b33dee5c2ee1208","tid":1510633,"uid":52817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T09:08:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NSAWdB2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNSAWdB2.jpg&h=7e1fa5a5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"88694c00eb661eb661c45f272788fe049ed58ede","tid":1510633,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T09:09:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PWzcvgg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPWzcvgg.jpg&h=187c67d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=9rGlslGXeLGLpJWMZA8bi7eFZk%2BLn%2Bp4m9s6a9hK%2BPA%3D&h=d3ee6c98\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=9rGlslGXeLGLpJWMZA8bi7eFZk%2BLn%2Bp4m9s6a9hK%2BPA%3D&h=baee3934\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=9rGlslGXeLGLpJWMZA8bi7eFZk%2BLn%2Bp4m9s6a9hK%2BPA%3D&h=4deed4f1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"aa2b4781fd193ca6b455e732ee7e81b40080eb7e","tid":1510633,"uid":273916,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2